                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9664" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2413</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">672 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">集采压价？北陆反手掏2亿：买来的转型更香！</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Centralized Procurement Driving Down Prices? Beilu Pharmaceutical Strikes Back with 200 Million: Transformation through Acquisition Proves More Rewarding!</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">唐俐，邱欣悦，沈惠香</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京北陆药业股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北陆药业；收购；战略转型；集采政策；双轮驱动</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Beilu Pharmaceutical; acquisition; strategic transformation; centralized procurement policy; dual-wheel drive</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，北陆药业在医药行业集采降价潮的压力下，积极通过收购实现战略转型。特别是2024年，北陆药业斥资2.02亿元收购天原药业80%股权，引发行业关注。本案例首先对北陆药业的发展历程、收购前的业务困境及收购天原药业的背景进行了介绍。随后，阐述了北陆药业在收购前依赖化药业务面临的集采挑战，核心产品利润空间被压缩、净利润连续下滑等问题。在案例主体内容即收购过程介绍中，本案例从北陆药业收购海昌药业构建“原料药+制剂”一体化战略出发，讲述了该战略的成效与困境，以及在此基础上收购天原药业实现“化药+中药”双轮驱动战略的转型过程。通过学习本案例，可以帮助学生掌握企业战略转型、产业整合相关知识，并且可以为其他面临行业政策冲击和业务转型困境的企业提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, under the pressure of the wave of centralized procurement and price reduction in the pharmaceutical industry, Beilu Pharmaceutical has actively achieved strategic transformation through acquisitions. Particularly in 2024, Beilu Pharmaceutical invested 202 million yuan to acquire an 80% stake in Tianyuan Pharmaceutical, which has drawn the attention of the industry. This case first introduces the development history of Beilu Pharmaceutical, its business dilemmas before the acquisition, and the background of the acquisition of Tianyuan Pharmaceutical. Subsequently, it expounds on the challenges of centralized procurement that Beilu Pharmaceutical faced before the acquisition due to its reliance on the chemical drug business, such as the compression of the profit margin of core products and the continuous decline of net profit. In the main content of the case, namely the introduction of the acquisition process, starting from the &quot;API + preparation&quot; integrated strategy established by Beilu Pharmaceutical through the acquisition of Haichang Pharmaceutical, this case narrates the effectiveness and dilemmas of this strategy, as well as the transformation process of achieving the &quot;chemical drug + traditional Chinese medicine&quot; dual-drive strategy through the acquisition of Tianyuan Pharmaceutical on this basis. By studying this case, students can master the relevant knowledge of corporate strategic transformation and industrial integration, and it can also provide references for other enterprises facing industry policy impacts and business transformation dilemmas.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">资源基础理论；集采；VRIO模型；协同效应理论；动态能力理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-06</td>
